    "rowsha": "1kG4qxRf/u32A4z60d0Wsfxn9/C2lNXovEmJL+v7cYA=",
    "originContent": "## Features and Contents",
    "translatedContent": "## 功能和内容"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "rk4Yh6Rr0Z9iOPNoWfBeXfTtQHafbrtkiuq3XZTbuvI=",
    "originContent": "- **TurboRepo**: The repository is configured to work with TurboRepo – a tool that simplifies the management of multiple interconnected repositories within a single project. This allows you to focus on feature development while TurboRepo handles organization.",
    "translatedContent": "- **TurboRepo**：该仓库配置为支持 TurboRepo —— 一个简化单个项目中多个相互关联仓库管理的工具。这样你可以专注于功能开发，而 TurboRepo 负责组织管理。"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "P4ccd4ppcWOrt8MqhHKIBAPWNZXr9A4P3EPwqfrjBJU=",
    "originContent": "- **NestJS**: The backend of the application is built on NestJS, a Node.js-based framework that enables the creation of scalable and modular APIs. Fully integrated with TypeScript, NestJS offers performance and readable code.",
    "translatedContent": "- **NestJS**：应用的后端基于 NestJS 构建，这是一个基于 Node.js 的框架，支持创建可扩展且模块化的 API。NestJS 完全集成 TypeScript，提供性能和可读性兼备的代码。"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "ILCIGZt2T+NAoLnS+xQDiA1lVPbR/ENVkb4pID4qQXg=",
    "originContent": "- **Vue 3 + Vite**: The user interface is based on Vue 3, the latest version of the popular JavaScript framework. We also use Vite, a fast and modern tool for building user interfaces.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Vue 3 + Vite**：用户界面基于 Vue 3，这是流行的 JavaScript 框架的最新版本。我们还使用了 Vite，一款快速且现代的用户界面构建工具。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "hS1pP/s1f8Wq+bs3BjUcjMnjnOrqJ6s5FMv9pLNjELs=",
    "originContent": "- **TypeScript**: The entire project is written in TypeScript, enhancing code safety and facilitating refactoring and maintenance.",
    "translatedContent": "- **TypeScript**：整个项目均使用 TypeScript 编写，提升代码安全性，方便重构和维护。"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "6viMgSftUUHY8TDspZW7eF0oc1HMHB+4yEdSgafBWKM=",
    "originContent": "- **Nuxt.js**: The repository also includes a sample configuration for Nuxt.js, a framework for creating Vue.js SSR (Server-Side Rendering) applications. This ensures SEO performance and fast content loading.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Nuxt.js**：该仓库还包含 Nuxt.js 的示例配置，Nuxt.js 是用于创建 Vue.js 服务器端渲染（SSR）应用的框架，确保 SEO 性能和内容快速加载。"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "97/eno8/B8/ChHCWQWmH0BOdeYgF3+FxEpw3n7pCKzo=",
    "originContent": "- **Electron**: The project can also be packaged as a desktop application using Electron, allowing you to create cross-platform applications.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Electron**：该项目也可以使用 Electron 打包为桌面应用程序，允许您创建跨平台应用。"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "3rIrqro+04W1KiZ3jFj4WrsPR869CbBia3lrqjUh/+Y=",
    "originContent": "- **Capacitor**: Capacitor is integrated to enable building native mobile apps using web technologies.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Capacitor**：集成了 Capacitor，以便使用 Web 技术构建原生移动应用。"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "CzHA0EtCtUS9EA7BsM9qITwMJq/0/F5aJlsVTH6yxtA=",
    "originContent": "- **Docker**: Docker is utilized to containerize and manage application deployment.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Docker**：使用 Docker 来容器化和管理应用程序部署。"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "vtwUILVmMkedjCmqrAJ8Yx9ZVa0tqen/3p3dzjgN/tY=",
    "originContent": "- **Shared Package**: The repository incorporates a shared package to enhance code reusability and maintainability.",
    "translatedContent": "- **共享包**：仓库中包含一个共享包，以增强代码的可复用性和可维护性。"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "hj5s48+6J0H/zsaNKnY37NZOin80fDMs7lOiens+3cQ=",
    "originContent": "- **Test Configuration with Vitest and Jest**: The repository includes a pre-configured setup for testing using Vitest and Jest. You can easily write and run unit tests for your Vue components and TypeScript code. Simply utilize the provided test configuration and harness the power of Vitest's rapid testing capabilities along with Jest's robust testing framework.",
    "translatedContent": "- **使用 Vitest 和 Jest 的测试配置**：仓库包含预配置的 Vitest 和 Jest 测试设置。您可以轻松编写并运行 Vue 组件和 TypeScript 代码的单元测试。只需利用提供的测试配置，结合 Vitest 的快速测试能力和 Jest 的强大测试框架。"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
